  <h1 class="art-title">Why Some People Prefer Simple Wellness Support Over Complicated Plans</h1>

  <div class="art-deck">
    A practical look at why simple wellness routines may feel more realistic than complicated lifestyle plans — and what research consistently shows about the power of doing less, better.
  </div>

