  <p>
    Across multiple fields — behavioral science, nutritional epidemiology, sleep research, and longevity studies — certain wellness principles emerge repeatedly as both effective and sustainable. They share one defining characteristic: they are simple enough to do every day, even when life gets complicated.
  </p>

