    </div>
    <div class="habit-card">
      <div class="hc-icon">🚶</div>
      <div class="hc-title">Low-Intensity Daily Movement</div>
      <div class="hc-text">20–40 minutes of walking each day outperforms sporadic intense exercise in every long-term metabolic outcome measure. It is also far more sustainable because it requires almost no willpower to initiate.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="habit-card">
      <div class="hc-icon">🍽️</div>
      <div class="hc-title">Add Before You Subtract</div>
      <div class="hc-text">Adding fiber, protein, and whole foods to meals — before focusing on eliminating anything — improves satiety, microbiome diversity, and metabolic markers without the cortisol spike that restriction produces.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="habit-card">
